BA%ADp-th%E1%BA%A5t-minh-ph%E1%BB%A7-chi-huy%E1%BB%87n/poem-FkFpO-EDNdin6aSwaVd7DA">Tống Triệu thập thất minh phủ chi huyện - 送趙十七明府之縣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/U-Ch%C3%A2u-H%E1%BB%93-m%C3%A3-kh%C3%A1ch-ca/poem-bTf_52UQUpmjhfVHO5qnaA">U Châu Hồ mã khách ca - 幽州胡馬客歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%E1%BB%8Dng-%C4%90%C3%A2u-Su%E1%BA%A5t-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-_Eivmua4HX5926slX_-2Ng">Vọng Đâu Suất tự - 望兜率寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-%C4%90%C3%A0o/V%E1%BB%8Dng-xu%C3%A2n-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-m2YhvfePbJXH4QrSUu3nvQ">Vọng xuân từ kỳ 4 - 春望詞其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-%C4%90%C3%A0o/author-YFc6G7OeOIRiUPVl88lFdA">Tiết Đào</a>)<br></div>	</div>
